(visitado)

00:15:37.879 --> 00:15:38.960
(Oficina del detective Hale)

00:15:39.159 --> 00:15:40.440
(y lo contrató)

00:15:40.600 --> 00:15:42.519
(para investigar a su marido)

00:15:42.639 --> 00:15:43.840
(El romance de Jackson.)

00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:44.960
(Pronto,)

00:15:45.039 --> 00:15:46.000
(Hale capturado...)

